headline: Midland County, Michigan, Completes Implementation of Tyler Technologies’ Public Safety Solutions
summary: PLANO, Texas, January 06, 2026--Tyler Technologies and the MCCDA in Michigan have completed the implementation of Tyler’s Enterprise Computer Aided Dispatch (CAD) solution.
